        <MudText Typo="Typo.h5" Class="mb-2">Access Control</MudText>
        <MudText Typo="Typo.body1">
            Access to Family Kitchen is controlled by invitation only. The household administrator manages 
            which email addresses are permitted to access the application.
        </MudText>
    </MudPaper>

    <MudPaper Class="pa-4 mb-4" Elevation="0">
        <MudText Typo="Typo.h5" Class="mb-2">Disclaimer</MudText>
        <MudText Typo="Typo.body1">
            Family Kitchen is provided "as is" without warranty of any kind. This is a personal project 
